Build instructions:
  unpack apache2-2.2.6-1-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  ./apache2-2.2.6-1.sh all

Or use './apache2-2.2.6-1.sh prep' to get a patched source directory

