Port Notes:

Patches:
Various miscellaneous buildsystem changes (httpd bug #33627)
Changes to build a seperate core shared library
Change the default pid file to httpd2.pid

A "2" was added to the names of many files, to avoid conflicting with the
same-named files from Apache 1.3.

